{"tid":1378958,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逃避並不可恥, 而且有用","createTime":"2019-07-28T17:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T12:38:57.000Z","uid":286864,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3632af19894df16f6c041cb9358454566e1d97a7","tid":1378958,"uid":286864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:10:33.000Z","msg":"結衣BB曰: 逃避雖然可恥, 但有用。<br />\n<img src=\"http://8maple.ru/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/179481.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F8maple.ru%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F10%2F179481.jpg&h=98d1c216&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n古今中外, 幾多英雄豪傑都係會經歷挫折, 逃跑雖然睇落唔風光, 但成大事者不拘小節, 不呈一時之氣, 睇啱時機逃下來, 不單可以<span style=\"color: red;\">保存實力</span>, 更有可能幫助<span style=\"color: red;\">看穿大局</span>, 以至能<span style=\"color: red;\">反敗為勝</span>都唔出奇!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例子:<br />\n1. 韓信忍過跨下之辱, 成就一代軍神。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%9F%A9%E4%BF%A1#%E6%97%A9%E6%9C%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%259F%25A9%25E4%25BF%25A1%23%25E6%2597%25A9%25E6%259C%259F&d=hFQF9A%2B1epMDho65PkJDL6jPH3pfKCXBWMLigY0rPLs%3D&h=c7b91782\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%9F%A9%E4%BF%A1#%E6%97%A9%E6%9C%9F</a><br />\n2. 鄧寇克戰役 (Battle of Dunkirk) 之中, 盟軍執行了當時最大規模的撤退行動，名為「發電機行動」, 成功挽救了將近40萬名盟軍士兵，並成為4年後反攻歐洲的根本。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%95%A6%E5%88%BB%E5%B0%94%E5%85%8B%E6%88%98%E5%BD%B9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%2595%25A6%25E5%2588%25BB%25E5%25B0%2594%25E5%2585%258B%25E6%2588%2598%25E5%25BD%25B9&d=hFQF9A%2B1epMDho65PkJDL6jPH3pfKCXBWMLigY0rPLs%3D&h=18599914\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%95%A6%E5%88%BB%E5%B0%94%E5%85%8B%E6%88%98%E5%BD%B9</a><br />\n3. 當然唔少得老毛魔既二萬五千里「長征」(走佬)啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%95%BF%E5%BE%81#%E5%85%B6%E5%AE%83%E8%A9%95%E5%83%B9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%2595%25BF%25E5%25BE%2581%23%25E5%2585%25B6%25E5%25AE%2583%25E8%25A9%2595%25E5%2583%25B9&d=hFQF9A%2B1epMDho65PkJDL6jPH3pfKCXBWMLigY0rPLs%3D&h=716bf9cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%95%BF%E5%BE%81#%E5%85%B6%E5%AE%83%E8%A9%95%E5%83%B9</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以撒退並唔等於戰敗, 逃避都並唔可恥, 於棄先至係真正可恥!!!!</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港, 時代革命!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5ec2bce148ec76d86d976a63b0bdf8996b5b09","tid":1378958,"uid":286864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:38:57.000Z","msg":"留得青山在！"}]}